translate Japanese ch2_main_ad37319b:

    # "Glorius morning."
    "最高の目覚めだ。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:6
translate Japanese ch2_main_1be144d5:

    # "Except the nightmare tortured me and pooled me into sweat."
    "夢にうなされてびっしょり寝汗をかいた以外は本当に最高だ。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:8
translate Japanese ch2_main_27cb115d:

    # "I take a shower quickly and put the uniform on."
    "さっとシャワーを済ませ、制服に着替える。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:8
translate Japanese ch2_main_4f704159:

    # "I should have some breakfast, anyway."
    "何か食べたほうがいいかな。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:12
translate Japanese ch2_main_4b79d09b:

    # "I come to the kitchen, but I'm not so hungry."
    "キッチンに来たものの、食欲はあまりない。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:12
translate Japanese ch2_main_51d60d5f:

    # "(Sigh)"
    "はあ……。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:13
translate Japanese ch2_main_2d03209a:

    # "Because I've got knot in my stomach."
    "心晴れやかといえば嘘になる。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:14
translate Japanese ch2_main_e02a931e:

    # "About Sayori, of course."
    "もちろんサヨリのことだ。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:15
translate Japanese ch2_main_e9d2e45c:

    # "She said that her rainclouds haven't gone yet."
    "結局のところ、あいつの言う「雨雲」を晴らすことを、自分はできなかった。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:16
translate Japanese ch2_main_7aff6cc0:

    # "But, what can I do for her?"
    "かと言って、何が自分にできるんだろう？"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:17
translate Japanese ch2_main_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:18
translate Japanese ch2_main_717a6fcb:

    # "Does she skip breakfast so often?"
    "あいつ、ちゃんと朝食べてるのかな。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:19
translate Japanese ch2_main_d65dd71b:

    # "I don't think she's good at cooking."
    "どう考えても、料理が得意なタイプじゃないよな。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:21
translate Japanese ch2_main_d6ccaf2c:

    # "I also doubt if she can just cut the vegetable."
    "野菜切るのもまともにできそうにない。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:21
translate Japanese ch2_main_d4409149:

    # "Neither can I, but I don't think I'm worse than her."
    "俺だって得意じゃない。でもあいつよりはマシなはずだ。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:22
translate Japanese ch2_main_ccf44ca8:

    # "Like, chopping green onion. It's not so hard for me."
    "ネギを刻むくらいなら問題ない。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:23
translate Japanese ch2_main_a89f3e82:

    # "If I could make a miso-soup for her in the morning,"
    "たとえば、あいつにできたての味噌汁でも作ってあげられたら、"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:24
translate Japanese ch2_main_5d90d690:

    # "She might feel happy, at least she would eat it."
    "もしかしたら喜んでくれるかもしれない。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:25
translate Japanese ch2_main_9cb8a6f0:

    # "I took a kitchen knife in the hand."
    "俺はキッチンナイフを手にする。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:26
translate Japanese ch2_main_669ec01b:

    # "I take a kitchen knife in the hand."
    "俺はキッチンナイフを手にする。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:27
translate Japanese ch2_main_3c7013e2:

    # "I look at it, and my train of thoughts go..."
    "それを見つめながら、俺は考える。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:27
translate Japanese ch2_main_7755bcc5:

    # "Umm... When did I cook something last time?"
    "最後に料理したのっていつだっけ？"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:28
translate Japanese ch2_main_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:29
translate Japanese ch2_main_a20cefa7_2:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:30
translate Japanese ch2_main_a20cefa7_3:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:31
translate Japanese ch2_main_a20cefa7_4:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:32
translate Japanese ch2_main_f6406039:

    # "...Oh shit."
    "……おっと。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:33
translate Japanese ch2_main_f171e72c:

    # "I was spacing out for... how long? I'm late."
    "どれくらいぼんやりしていたのか。このままだと遅刻する。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:34
translate Japanese ch2_main_5cac6d8b:

    # "I shurugged and picked up my school bag."
    "雑念を振り払うように頭を振って、かばんを手にする。"

# game/script-ddmc-ch2.rpy:35
translate Japanese ch2_main_02326689:

    # "I shurug and pick up my school bag."
    "雑念を振り払うように頭を振って、かばんを手にする。"

# game/script-ch2.rpy:35
translate Japanese ch2_main_b0aacee5:

    # "Good bye my breakfast, again."
    "結局、今日も朝メシは抜きだ。"

